OL,3,CHundreds of jobs at risk as Bentley
OL,4,Cannounces overhaul
OL,6,FLuxury carmaker Bentley has warned
OL,7,Faround 275 jobs are at risk as part of
OL,8,Fa company restructure.
OL,10,FThe group, which makes its cars in
OL,11,FCrewe, Cheshire, said it was as a
OL,12,Fresult of an "organisational
OL,13,Fadjustment" to help make savings.
OL,15,FIt said the cuts ` which account for
OL,16,Faround 6% of its 4,600-strong
OL,17,Fworkforce in Crewe ` would affect
OL,18,Fmanagement, agency and other office-
OL,19,Fbased roles, but not manufacturing
OL,20,Fjobs.
OL,26,@tD@NOUuD@KO]
