CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773839493
OL,3,CHundreds of jobs at risk as Bentley
OL,4,Cannounces overhaul
OL,6,FThe cuts will impact 150 staff, who
OL,7,Fhave been placed at risk of
OL,8,Fredundancy, with another 125 roles
OL,9,Fexpected to go through not replacing
OL,10,Ftemporary workers, staff turnover and
OL,11,Fnot filling some vacancies.
OL,13,FIt is consulting over the 150
OL,14,Fredundancies over the next four to six
OL,15,Fweeks, while the wider role cuts are
OL,16,Fset to be made by the end of the year.
OL,18,FKaren Lewis, GMB organiser, said:
OL,19,F"These cuts have come out of the blue
OL,20,Fand the workforce is stunned.
OL,26,@{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
