OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773839493
OL,3,CHundreds of jobs at risk as Bentley
OL,4,Cannounces overhaul
OL,6,F"Trump's tariff's have hit Bentley
OL,7,Fhard and the company is still feeling
OL,8,Fthe affects of the Covid lockdown.
OL,10,F"GMB will stand side by side with
OL,11,Fmembers in Bentley to ensure the
OL,12,Fminimum redundancies and the maximum
OL,13,Fpayouts."
OL,15,FBentley Chairman and Chief Executive
OL,16,FFrank-Steffen Walliser said: "We are
OL,17,Fmaking some difficult decisions to
OL,18,Fensure the long-term competitiveness
OL,19,Fof the business, including an
OL,20,Forganisational adjustment potentially
OL,21,Fimpacting approximately 275 positions.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@IO]xD@^OU
