PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1773839493
OL,3,CHundreds of jobs at risk as Bentley
OL,4,Cannounces overhaul
OL,6,F"I want to express my sincere
OL,7,Fappreciation to those affected ` we
OL,8,Fare committed to supporting each
OL,9,Findividual with care, guidance and
OL,10,Fassistance throughout this transition."
OL,12,FThe planned job losses were revealed
OL,13,Fas Bentley announced a 42% drop in
OL,14,Fannual operating profits to 216
OL,15,Fmillion euros (#186.6 million) as it
OL,16,Fsaid it faced "a challenging global
OL,17,Fmarket environment".
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@gO]xD@OOUyD@SO]
