OL,3,CHundreds of jobs at risk as Bentley
OL,4,Cannounces overhaul
OL,6,FIt said its performance came under
OL,7,Fpressure due to higher costs from
OL,8,Fchanges at its parent company
OL,9,FVolkswagen and a 42 million euro
OL,10,F(#36.3 million) hit from US tariffs.
